metadata.name: Break a leg
metadata.description:
"Break a leg" is an AI-generated artwork exploring idioms through the lens of artificial intelligence. It captures colorful and quirky phrases, offering a playful and thought-provoking interpretation of these expressions.

𝗦𝗽𝗲𝗰𝗶𝗮𝗹 𝗲𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝗳𝗼𝗿 𝗦𝘂𝗽𝗲𝗿𝗰𝗵𝗶𝗲𝗳 & 𝗘𝘅𝗾𝘂𝗶𝘀𝗶𝘁𝗲 𝗪𝗼𝗿𝗸𝗲𝗿𝘀
Created for AI Surrealism Show, NY with 100 artists
Released on June 2-8, 2023
